pintMib.description: This MIB defines the objects necessary to monitor PINT Services

PintServiceType.name: PintServiceType
PintServiceType.description: This TC describes the type of a PINT service.

PintPerfStatPeriod.name: PintPerfStatPeriod
PintPerfStatPeriod.description: This TC describes the statistics period of time. Note that the values of the counters indexed with a value SinceReboot(4) can be potentially affected by a counter rollover. It is the responsibility of the application using this object to take into account that the counter has been zeroed each time it reached a value of (2**32-1).

pintReleaseNumber.name: pintReleaseNumber
pintReleaseNumber.description: An indication of version of the PINT protocol supported by this agent.

pintSysContact.name: pintSysContact
pintSysContact.description: Contact information related to the administration of the PINT services.

pintApplInstallPkgTable.name: pintApplInstallPkgTable
pintApplInstallPkgTable.description: Table describing the PINT applications that are installed.

pintApplInstallPkgDescription.name: pintApplInstallPkgDescription
pintApplInstallPkgDescription.description: Textual description of the installed PINT application.

pintRegisteredGatewayTable.name: pintRegisteredGatewayTable
pintRegisteredGatewayTable.description: Table describing the registered gateway applications.

pintRegisteredGatewayDescription.name: pintRegisteredGatewayDescription
pintRegisteredGatewayDescription.description: Textual description of the registered gateway.

pintServerGlobalStatsTable.name: pintServerGlobalStatsTable
pintServerGlobalStatsTable.description: Table displaying the monitored global server statistics.

pintServerGlobalStatsEntry.name: pintServerGlobalStatsEntry
pintServerGlobalStatsEntry.description: Entries in the global statistics table. One entry is defined for each monitored service type and performance statistics collection period.

pintServerServiceTypeIndex.name: pintServerServiceTypeIndex
pintServerServiceTypeIndex.description: The unique identifier of the monitored service.

pintServerPerfStatPeriodIndex.name: pintServerPerfStatPeriodIndex
pintServerPerfStatPeriodIndex.description: Time period for which the performance statistics are requested from the pint server.

pintServerGlobalDisCUAutFCalls.name: pintServerGlobalDisCUAutFCalls
pintServerGlobalDisCUAutFCalls.description: Number of global calls that were disconnected because of client or user authorization failure.

pintServerGlobalDisServProbCalls.name: pintServerGlobalDisServProbCalls
pintServerGlobalDisServProbCalls.description: Number of global calls that were disconnected because of server problems.

pintServerGlobalDisGatProbCalls.name: pintServerGlobalDisGatProbCalls
pintServerGlobalDisGatProbCalls.description: Number of global calls that were disconnected because of gateway problems.

pintServerClientStatsTable.name: pintServerClientStatsTable
pintServerClientStatsTable.description: Table displaying the monitored server client statistics.

pintServerClientStatsEntry.name: pintServerClientStatsEntry
pintServerClientStatsEntry.description: Entries in the client server statistics table. One entry is defined for each client identified by name, monitored service type and performance statistics collection period.

pintServerClientAddress.name: pintServerClientAddress
pintServerClientAddress.description: The unique identifier of the monitored client identified by its address represented as as a string.

pintServerClientCallsReceived.name: pintServerClientCallsReceived
pintServerClientCallsReceived.description: Number of calls received from the specific client.

pintServerClientSuccessfulCalls.name: pintServerClientSuccessfulCalls
pintServerClientSuccessfulCalls.description: Number of calls from the client successfully completed.

pintServerClientDisconnectedCalls.name: pintServerClientDisconnectedCalls
pintServerClientDisconnectedCalls.description: Number of calls received from the client, and that were disconnected (failed).

pintServerClientDisCAutFCalls.name: pintServerClientDisCAutFCalls
pintServerClientDisCAutFCalls.description: Number of calls from the client that were disconnected because of client authorization failure.

pintServerClientDisEFProbCalls.name: pintServerClientDisEFProbCalls
pintServerClientDisEFProbCalls.description: Number of calls from the client that were disconnected because of egress facility problems.

pintServerUserIdStatsTable.name: pintServerUserIdStatsTable
pintServerUserIdStatsTable.description: Table displaying the monitored Pint service user statistics.

pintServerUserIdStatsEntry.name: pintServerUserIdStatsEntry
pintServerUserIdStatsEntry.description: Entries in the user statistics table. One entry is defined for each user identified by name, each monitored service type and performance statistics collection period. It is assumed that the capabilities of the pint server are enough to accommodate the number of entries in this table. It is a local server implementation issue if an aging mechanism Is implemented in order to avoid scalability problems.

pintServerUserIdName.name: pintServerUserIdName
pintServerUserIdName.description: The unique identifier of the monitored user identified by its name.

pintServerUserIdCallsReceived.name: pintServerUserIdCallsReceived
pintServerUserIdCallsReceived.description: Number of calls received from the specific user.

pintServerUserIdSuccessfulCalls.name: pintServerUserIdSuccessfulCalls
pintServerUserIdSuccessfulCalls.description: Number of calls from the user successfully completed.

pintServerUserIdDisconnectedCalls.name: pintServerUserIdDisconnectedCalls
pintServerUserIdDisconnectedCalls.description: Number of calls received from the user that were disconnected (failed).

pintServerUserIdDiscUIdAFailCalls.name: pintServerUserIdDiscUIdAFailCalls
pintServerUserIdDiscUIdAFailCalls.description: Number of calls from the user that were disconnected because of user authorization failure.

pintServerUserIdEFProbCalls.name: pintServerUserIdEFProbCalls
pintServerUserIdEFProbCalls.description: Number of calls from the user that were disconnected because of egress facility problems.

pintServerGatewayStatsTable.name: pintServerGatewayStatsTable
pintServerGatewayStatsTable.description: Table displaying the monitored gateway statistics.

pintServerGatewayStatsEntry.name: pintServerGatewayStatsEntry
pintServerGatewayStatsEntry.description: Entries in the gateway table. One entry is defined for each gateway identified by name, each monitored service type and performance statistics collection period.

pintServerGatewayCallsReceived.name: pintServerGatewayCallsReceived
pintServerGatewayCallsReceived.description: Number of calls received at the specified gateway.

pintServerGatewaySuccessfulCalls.name: pintServerGatewaySuccessfulCalls
pintServerGatewaySuccessfulCalls.description: Number of calls successfully completed at the specified gateway.

pintServerGatewayDisconnectedCalls.name: pintServerGatewayDisconnectedCalls
pintServerGatewayDisconnectedCalls.description: Number of calls that were disconnected (failed) at the specified gateway.

pintMibCompliance.name: pintMibCompliance
pintMibCompliance.description: Describes the requirements for conformance to the PINT MIB.

pintMibConfigGroup.name: pintMibConfigGroup
pintMibConfigGroup.description: A collection of objects providing configuration information for a PINT Server.

pintMibMonitorGroup.name: pintMibMonitorGroup
pintMibMonitorGroup.description: A collection of objects providing monitoring information for a PINT Server.
